1. *Kola* su nam bila potrebna da stignemo na vreme. (The car was necessary for us to arrive on time.) 
2. On je bio previše umoran da vozi *kolu*. (He was too tired to drive the car.)
3. *Kole* su se kretale polako. (The cars were moving slowly.)
4. Ona je otišla sa *kolom* u grad. (She went to town with the car.) 
5. *Kolu* je trebalo da održavamo. (The car had to be maintained.) 
6. On je kupio novu *kolu*. (He bought a new car.)